Title: live your own
DateModified: '2019-03-04'
DatePublished: '2019-03-04'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/live-your-own
SetInCountry: India
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: shweta kodam
AuthorCountry: India
Text: 'Destination Story

  The best story about a place that captures its essence and reveals its attractions,
  making the reader want to go there


  Adventure Travel

  The best story of high adventure, danger, or physical challenge


  Bad Trip

  The best account of when things go wrong, or the shadow side of a culture or individual


  Travel and Food

  The best story where food or drink plays a role in introducing the traveler to a
  foreign culture or new friends


  Family Travel

  The best story about traveling with family of all generations grandparents, parents,
  children, cousins, siblings or journeying to discover roots


  Love Story: The best account of love or romance on the road'
